      "content": "It's okay to feel that way, but remember, stepping off the path doesn't mean you're done with a journey. It might just be a different kind of adventure, one that doesn't involve traveling to new places. Sometimes, the most profound discoveries happen when we stop moving and start reflecting. This could be the perfect time to explore new hobbies, deepen connections with loved ones, or simply enjoy the peace that comes from knowing you've seen what you've always wanted to see. Life has many paths, even if they aren't marked on a map.",
      "source": "target",
